\n- Which subagent phases had the most tool calls?\n- Which subagents read the same files repeatedly?\n- Which Bash commands produced the largest outputs?\n- What redundant operations were reported?\nInclude this subagent-level breakdown in the cost analysis section.\n\nThis is Session 63, a NO-OP session. The sprint is 100% complete (74/74 stories, 17/17 epics all done). The ONLY work this session did was fix state corruption #47 — stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review` by Ralph's stale in-memory state, and the orchestrator fixed them back to `done`. This pattern has repeated 47 times.\n\nProduce a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — no-op session, state corruption fix only\n2. **Issues analysis** — the critical Ralph stale-state bug that has wasted 47+ sessions\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report, estimate waste from repeated no-op sessions\n4. **What went well** — sprint is 100% complete\n5. **What went wrong** — 47 consecutive wasted sessions on same bug\n6. **Lessons learned** — Ralph needs a sprint-complete exit condition\n7. **Action items** — stop Ralph, fix stale-state overwrite, add exit condition\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md. Since a retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"af7c688161803907e","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Retrospective for Session 63 appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md`.\n\nKey findings:\n- **$743.63 total spend**, estimated **$315 wasted (42%)** on 47 identical no-op sessions\n- Same bug every time: Ralph's stale in-memory state reverts stories 16-5/6/7/8 from `done` to `review`\n- Sprint has been 100% complete since session 17 — 47 sessions of pure waste\n- P0 action: stop Ralph, add `done`-is-terminal guard, add sprint-complete exit condition"}],"totalDurationMs":73160,"totalTokens":29453,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2112,"cache_read_input_tokens":27165,"output_tokens":175,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2112},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
